window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Dying is easy. Coming back is the hard part.</p> <p>After shattering his soul during a spell, Lazarus has just six days to find the pieces and put them back together. Not an easy task when every reaper in the underworld is gunning to claim his soul, including the reaper king, Thanatos.</p> <p>To reclaim the lost fragments of his soul, he'll have to face old enemies, travel to Faerie to battle his most fearsome foe yet, and acquire a vast sum of sugary snack cakes. If he fails, more than his own life is on the line. Mask is amassing an army to retake Earth and snuff out all life forever.</p> <p>Can Lazarus pull himself together in time to save the world one more time?</p>"; 
